name: Franco Oscar
description: I am looking for someone who can make me laugh. I am an active person who loves to dance and regularly hits the gym. Would love someone to go to the movies with and have a wonderful night out….I would like to spend time with a partner who I can talk with. I am also a great cook! If we get to know each other good enough…. I am not looking for just a lover, but also for companionship. Someone I can have an educated conversation with.
